## Architecture Overview

CORTEX uses a 4-tier cognitive architecture:

| Tier | Purpose | Storage | Update Frequency |
|------|---------|---------|------------------|
| **Tier 0** | Governance & Rules | YAML (immutable) | Never (protected) |
| **Tier 1** | Working Memory | SQLite (FIFO queue) | Every conversation |
| **Tier 2** | Knowledge Graph | SQLite (FTS5) | Pattern learning |
| **Tier 3** | Context Intelligence | SQLite (analytics) | Project analysis |

